Hymn.Arabic: قُوَّتِي وَتَسْبِحَتِي هُوَ الرَّبُّ ، وَقَدْ صَارَ لِي خَلَاصًا.
Hymn.English: 14 The Lord is my strength and song, And He has become my salvation.

Hymn.Arabic: أَدَبًا أَدَّبَنِي الرَّبُّ ، وَإِلَى الْمَوْتِ لَمْ يُسْلِمْنِي. هَلِّلُويَا.
Hymn.English: 18 The Lord has chastened me severely, But He has not given me over to death.     Alleluia
